element.name: TCustomPage
element.descr: Custom Page: The base type for Page

element.name: TNBPages
element.descr: NB Pages: The set of instances of Notebook Page

element.name: TCustomNotebook
element.descr: Custom Notebook: The base type for Notebook

element.name: TPage
element.descr: Page: One of the pages in a tabbed Notebook

element.name: TNotebook
element.descr: Notebook: A series of tabbed pages placed together to make a notebook

element.name: TTimer
element.descr: Timer: An elapsed timer useful in many applications

element.name: TIdleTimer
element.descr: Idle Timer: A timer to measure idle time between processes

element.name: TShape
element.descr: Shape: An arbitrary graphic geometrical shape placed on the Form. It may be one of a series of standard shapes defined by TShapeType

element.name: TCustomSplitter
element.descr: Custom Splitter: the base type for Splitter

element.name: TSplitter
element.descr: Splitter: A vertical or horizontal bar that can be placed on a panel or form, to separate sub-panels functionally and allow re-sizing of the constituent sub-panels

element.name: TPaintBox
element.descr: Paint Box: A tool for generating pictures

element.name: TCustomImage
element.descr: Custom Image: The base type for Image

element.name: TImage
element.descr: Image: A graphic image placed on the form; usually loaded from a picture file

element.name: TImage.Picture
element.descr: Picture: the actual graphical image to be displayed

element.name: TBevel
element.descr: A bevel placed around the edge of buttons and other components. Its appearance is governed by TBevelShape, TBevelStyle and TBevelwidth

element.name: TCustomRadioGroup
element.descr: Custom Radio Group: the base type for Radio Group

element.name: TRadioGroup
element.descr: Radio Group: A group of related but mutually exclusive radio buttons, requiring the user to select one af a set of alternatives

element.name: TCustomCheckGroup
element.descr: Custom Check Group: The base type for Check Group

element.name: TCheckGroup
element.descr: Checck Group: A group of Check Boxes physically and logically grouped together on a form

element.name: TCheckGroup.Caption
element.descr: Caption: the string which appears as a caption to describe the function of the Check Group

element.name: TBoundLabel
element.descr: Bound Label: A label bound to another object, for example in Labelled Edit

element.name: TBoundLabel.Caption
element.descr: Caption : the caption which will appear on the Bound Label, to identify its function

element.name: TCustomLabeledEdit
element.descr: Cuatom Labelled Edit: The base type for Labelled Edit. Note particularly the EditLabel property (see TBoundLabel).

element.name: TLabeledEdit
element.descr:
Labelled Edit: An Edit Box with a permanently attached Label;
saves time and effort over placing separate Label and Edit Box on Form. The Label property is described in the parent component, TCustomLabeledEdit

element.name: TLabeledEdit.Text
element.descr: Text: the text-string being entered or edited in the Labelled Edit box

element.name: TCustomPanel
element.descr: Custom Panel: The base type for Panel

element.name: TPanel
element.descr: Panel: A defined rectangular area of the form into which other components can be placed to group them functionally and geographically
